# Lock byte-identity for the embedded agent-skill mirror. internal/agentskill/data/
# is a SHA256-verified mirror of mcamp/docs/nvcf/one-click-deploy/agent-skill/;
# auto-CRLF / BOM injection on Windows checkouts would corrupt the bytes and
# break the manifest verification chain. -text disables line-ending conversion;
# -crlf is the equivalent for older Git versions.
internal/agentskill/data/** -text -crlf
